transcript:
Executive: Hello?
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Haan ji, Adhyam Healthcare mein baat ho rahi hai?
Customer: Boliye.
Executive: Ji sir, ye Niyama team se baat kar rahi hu. Actually hamara na discussion hona tha sir pending hai abhi tak.
Customer: Achcha.
Executive: To wohi aapne time de rakha tha. To abhi baat ho sakti hai kya sir?
Customer: Nahi, main abhi main working se wapas aa raha hu, driving kar raha hu.
Executive: Achcha.
Customer: Hmm hmm.
Executive: To phir bataye kab matlab kyunki catalogue jo hai na usme hi problem aa raha tha aapke.
Customer: Haan, to wohi sara ek baar.
Executive: Kal morning mein?
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Theek hai, kal morning mein ek baar main aapko connect karti hu.
Customer: Okay.
